-- Mercapital to Buy 70% of Rubaiyat Steakhouse, Veja Reports
-- B y   B l a k e   S c h m i d t
-- 2012-07-28T13:57:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-28/mercapital-to-buy-70-of-rubaiyat-steakhouse-veja-reports.html
Brazilian steakhouse chain Rubaiyat
agreed to sell a 70 percent stake to Mercapital SL for
46 million euros ($56.7 million), the Sao Paulo-based weekly
 Veja  reported.  Belarmino Fernandez Iglesias Filho, head of Rubayait
restaurants, said he signed the deal this week with Madrid-based
Mercapital private equity, Veja says.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blake Schmidt in Bogota at 
 bschmidt16@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sylvia Wier in  New York  at 
 swier@bloomberg.net  